STATE
v.
Glenn Devon McKINNEY. No. 622PA05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 15, 2006. William B. Crumpler, Assistant Attorney General, R. Stuart Albright, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 14th day of March 2006 by Defendant for Extension of Time to File Brief:

"Motion Denied. Defendant (Glenn Devon McKinney) shall have up to and including the 29th day of March 2006 to file and serve his/her brief with this Court. By order of the Court in conference this the 15th day of March 2006."
